Project: Personal Expense Tracker
Features:
Add New Expenses:

Input fields for the expense name, amount, and date.
A button to add the expense to the list.
View Expense List:

Display a list of all added expenses with their details.
Option to sort by date or amount.
Edit and Delete Expenses:

Edit existing expense details.
Delete expenses from the list.
Calculate Totals:

Display the total amount spent and, optionally, categorize expenses (e.g., food, entertainment).
Responsive Design:

Ensure the UI works well on both desktop and mobile devices.
Data Persistence:

Use localStorage to save expenses so they persist when the page is refreshed.